text.tspan: Estimated number of deaths from earthquakes, World
Estimated number of annual deaths from earthquake events. This includes deaths from the earthquake plus those
from secondary impacts (such as a tsunami triggered by an earthquake). Due to data availability, reporting and
evidence, it's expected that more recent data will be more complete than the long historical record. A trend in reported
estimates therefore doesn't necessarily reflect the true change over time.
Source: National Geophysical Data Center (NGDC) of the NOAA
